en_US: ShopQ will verify your phone number. Note that phone number should be on this device in order to be verified. Enter your country code and phone number:
Sorry, but you can't order one hour before the shop's closing time

Choose the most convenient time for you and write a list of products that you need. After that, if the shop has all of the products on the list, the administrator will confirm that and you will see it on your app. If something is missing, administrator will contact you. You will see QR code on your screen, which you have to use when you get to the shop to claim and pay for your products.
Things to keep in mind: 
 1) You can't order one hour before the store is closing
 2) You can grab your products in the period of 15 minutes from your chosen time
 3) Be safe :)
